To play Astrostein 3, follow these instructions:1. Make a copy of the Wolfenstein 3D application and keep it in your Wolfenstein 3D folder. 2. Open the copy of the Wolfenstein 3D application with ResEdit.3. Find the "csnd" and "snd" pickers and delete them (deleting all the resources in them).4. Open the "Resources" ResEdit file supplied with Astrostein 3.5. Select all the pickers in this file, copy them, then paste them into the copy of Wolfenstein 3D. Answer "yes" when asked if you wish to replace resources with the same ID numbers.6. Save changes and quit ResEdit.7. Put the Astrostein 3 level file in the Levels folder in your Wolfenstein 3D folder.8. Launch the copy of Wolfenstein 3D and select the Astrostein 3 scenario.